node_modules
node/dist/
.env
go/.env
*.local
*.log
*.sip
*.pcap
*.cap
.planning/

# Built Go binaries (produced by `go build ./cmd/...` without -o)
/go/lint-metrics
/go/sipgate-sip-stream-bridge

# Operator UI (ui/) — single vite bundle, generated by `make ui` and copied into
# each backend by `make ui-go` / `make ui-node`.
/ui/dist/
# Embedded Go bundle: ignore everything generated by `make ui-go` (hashed
# assets, favicon, the real index.html) but keep the committed placeholder
# go/internal/web/dist/index.html so `//go:embed dist` always compiles on a
# fresh checkout. CI rebuilds the real bundle before the image build.
/go/internal/web/dist/*
!/go/internal/web/dist/index.html
